n\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17068,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/01\/barakah-fill-rows-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":42060,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Allah blesses those who fill prayer rows","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 1, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah and His angels send blessings upon those who connect the rows of prayer, and those who fill the gaps will be raised a degree by Allah.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 995 Grade: Hasan (fair) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23227,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/06\/14\/blessed-right-side-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":42060,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Blessing on the right side of prayer rows","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 14, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah and His angels send blessings upon those on the right side of the prayer rows.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 676 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Ibn Hajar \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u06